	(2203,515,'activities_2_activity_description','We will craft a setting for each of the participants to respond to some questions.\r\n\r\nJohn and Julian will answer questions from Dom OConnell on the Today Programme and Ellen will answer questions from Nicky Campbell on BBC Radio Five Live. Each will be about a broader issue and perhaps also focusing into their own work. They will each have time to prepare using support from Paul, Deborah and Paula as required.'),
