	(6163,759,'components_0_copy','This is your coaching portal.\r\n\r\nIf your session is coming up you can look at your<a href=\"http://portal.bladedev.co.uk/myagenda\">agenda</a>. This will tell you the timings and location of the session, as well as an outline of how it will run.\r\n\r\nYou will get even more out of your session if the coaches know a little more about you. So wed be really grateful if you could fill in this<a href=\"/questionnaire\">questionnaire</a> it will take less than 5 minutes, we promise.\r\n\r\nIf youve already had your session, we hope you enjoyed it. You can watch your<a href=\"/videogallery\">videos</a>, and read your<a href=\"/myfeedback\">feedback note</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you need us again or have any questions, you can always contact us.\r\n\r\nKind regards\r\n\r\nThe Bladonmore Team'),
