	(2084,503,'activities_5_activity_description','Ian is highly supportive of business but dislikes both over-zealous regulators and scoundrels and Kay Burley is a womens rights campaigner and feminist with strong views on domestic abuse and violence against women. For each of the interviews, we will agree on a story hook and the Bladonmore coaches will extemporise the kinds of questions that Ian would ask; again, Julian and John will have some time to prep.\r\n\r\nThese are live studio interviews.'),
