	(2855,571,'activities_3_activity_description','The next interview is intended to be an on-the-record interview in which Hugues will need to be very careful with what he says on sensitive issues. This interview will be videoed but we are likely to provide verbal only feedback. This will help manage time and reflect the way journalists goes through their notes to identify the best quotes. Topics may include\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hugues assessment of the main themes of MWC</li>\r\n 	<li>Huawei</li>\r\n 	<li>OCD ambitions</li>\r\n</ul>'),
