	(3668,602,'activities_4_activity_start','15:30:00'),
	(3669,602,'_activities_4_activity_start','field_5b11105bbe3d5'),
	(3670,602,'activities_4_activity_end','16:15:00'),
	(3671,602,'_activities_4_activity_end','field_5b111097bf5d2'),
	(3672,602,'activities_5_activity_name','Exercise 4: Press Conferences'),
	(3673,602,'_activities_5_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(3674,602,'activities_5_activity_description','We will ask the groups to decide on a chair and a subject matter. We suggest that BCL Solicitors advice on the growing concerns regarding privacy and cybersecurity threats. We will conduct two short press conferences and ask each group to become press reporters and fire questions at the other and then swap over.\r\n\r\nThis will give delegates the chance to work together and consolidate all the learning points, regarding giving regional angles to local press reporters and using the vocabulary that will work for each publication. It also gives us the opportunity to advise delegates on the importance of performance - even in a press setting - as well as content and presenting as a united front when representing BCL Solicitors on a public platform.'),
