	(3727,603,'activities_3_activity_name','Exercise 2:  Building Relationships: Briefing a new journalist at Law 360  the effect of Brexit on the law and European Arrest Warrant'),
	(3728,603,'_activities_3_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(3729,603,'activities_3_activity_description','The Bladonmore coaches and Myddleton team will explain the value of helping a journalist to get stories published. Its also important to gain their trust so that BCL Solicitors becomes a go-to source for background and ultimately comment, leading to comments in the nationals and articles in the trade press and raising awareness in the trade press.\r\n\r\nWe will give the groups time to work on a briefing and deliver it. We will film and review the two briefing sessions.'),
