	(4389,619,'activities_2_activity_name','Interview 1: Background briefing on OCD strategy with the FT at MWC'),
	(4390,619,'_activities_2_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(4391,619,'activities_2_activity_description','This interview will touch on the same themes as the WSJ interview and will be videoed and played back for constructive feedback\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The credibility of OCDs number 1 in Europe ambition</li>\r\n 	<li>How much money Hugues has to spend</li>\r\n 	<li>Whether the cyber-security market is inherently fragmented and therefore impossible to consolidate profitably</li>\r\n 	<li>What advantages Telcos have in providing cyber-security</li>\r\n 	<li>Orange Group Strategy</li>\r\n 	<li>Huawei</li>\r\n</ul>'),
	(4392,619,'_activities_2_activity_description','field_5b11098d14d46'),
	(4393,619,'activities_2_activity_start','15:30:00'),
	(4394,619,'_activities_2_activity_start','field_5b11105bbe3d5'),
	(4395,619,'activities_2_activity_end','16:10:00'),
	(4396,619,'_activities_2_activity_end','field_5b111097bf5d2'),
	(4397,619,'activities_3_activity_name','Interview 2: Interview with Bloomberg '),
	(4398,619,'_activities_3_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(4399,619,'activities_3_activity_description','The next interview is intended to be an on-the-record interview in which Hugues will need to be very careful with what he says on sensitive issues. This interview will be videoed but we are likely to provide verbal only feedback. This will help manage time and reflect the way journalists goes through their notes to identify the best quotes. Topics may include\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Hugues assessment of the main themes of MWC</li>\r\n 	<li>Huawei</li>\r\n 	<li>OCD ambitions</li>\r\n</ul>'),
	(4400,619,'_activities_3_activity_description','field_5b11098d14d46'),
	(4401,619,'activities_3_activity_start','16:10:00'),
	(4402,619,'_activities_3_activity_start','field_5b11105bbe3d5'),
	(4403,619,'activities_3_activity_end','16:30:00'),
	(4404,619,'_activities_3_activity_end','field_5b111097bf5d2'),
	(4405,619,'activities_4_activity_name','Interview 3: Video interviews with CNBC'),
	(4406,619,'_activities_4_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(4407,619,'activities_4_activity_description','In the final phase we will do a series of video interviews from the perspective of CNBC. The formats will be a pre-recorded clip and a live down the line with the idea being to give Hugues a sense of the different demands of TV and video, so he can adjust his delivery style accordingly.\r\n\r\nIn terms of topics, we will take the best messaging to have emerged up to this point and make that the basis of the interviews to reduce preparation time and allow Hugues to focus on his body language and voice.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
