	(4520,625,'_activities_0_activity_name','field_5b11097814d45'),
	(4521,625,'activities_0_activity_description','The Bladonmore team will introduce themselves to and set some context for the session. Then the Myddleton team will make some comments about the nature of the work that we do and that the purpose of the coaching is to arm Harry, Richard, Guy and Shaul with the techniques and confidence to take advantage of media opportunities that will enable them to promote their own practices and the firms brand and also to take on active competitors in their market.'),
