	(5303,659,'activities_3_activity_description','In the next phase we will do a series of two interviews with selected participants, on the stage. Each interview will be from a different perspective, the first with TechCrunch, the second with the BBC. The idea is to give the group a sense of (a) the kinds of questions they could encounter and (b) the different requirements of a range of journalists  clearly network TV is materially different to a phone interview with TechCrunch. Each interview will be videoed and the footage played back for constructive review.'),
