	(5311,659,'activities_4_activity_description','Using what they have learned from the interviews on the stage, the participants will each interview each other for 3  5 minutes. This will give them a sense of what it is like to be a journalist, hungry for a story and how difficult it can be to stay on message when reporters are asking difficult or left-field questions.'),
