	(5777,711,'components_0_copy','<div>\r\n<div>Welcome Clarisa</div>\r\n<div>This is your coaching portal.</div>\r\n<div>If your session is coming up you can look at your agenda. This will tell you the timings and location of the session, as well as an outline of how it will run.</div>\r\n<div>You will get even more out of your session if the coaches know a little more about you. So wed be really grateful if you could fill in this questionnaire  it will take less than 5 minutes, we promise.</div>\r\n<div>If youve already had your session, we hope you enjoyed it. You can watch your videos, and read your feedback note.</div>\r\n<div>If you need us again or have any questions, you can always contact us.</div>\r\n<div>Kind regards</div>\r\n<div>The Bladonmore Team</div>\r\n</div>'),
