	(6093,206,'bio','Bladonmores coaching department is a fast-paced, complex and exciting place to work. I make sure we deliver the outcomes and level of excellence that we and our clients expect by meticulously planning and orchestrating a range of strategic and operational projects.\r\n\r\nBuilding strong, lasting and open relationships  with clients, suppliers and colleagues  is key to how we operate. I love getting to know our clients and their worlds; not only is it fascinating, its how we develop the strategies that help them to craft and then tell their best stories.\r\n\r\nI feel enormously privileged to have the trust of our clients, and it is an honour to have them come back to us time and again  its a sign that we get them; that we truly understand the challenges and opportunities they face. Seeing how people engage with our work and how we make a real difference to the way they communicate  that is what is incredibly rewarding.'),
