	(6099,679,'bio','I am fascinated by the art and science behind how to get effective responses to the work our clients do. And Im as ambitious for our future as I was when we set sail on 11th March 2002.\r\n\r\nI spend two-thirds of my time helping clients to refine their narrative and verbalise it as effectively as possible. This means constructively speaking truth to power every day. The other third is spent obsessing about our own organisational development, striving to develop an environment where careers can blossom.'),
